Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}decided long ago in the past{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:31.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tooi mukashi sou kimeteita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After failing to assassinate Big Mom,\NLuffy and the others were cornered.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bege transformed himself into a huge castle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, as the Big Mom Pirates\Ncame attacking,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Germa 66 fought back\Nusing their scientific technology.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should retreat too-rero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the whole team took shelter in the castle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, their attacks were blocked\Nand on top of that, the castle is stuck.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Cutting the Father-Son Relationship!\NSanji and Judge!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll start killing anyone who steps out...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just come out already!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you have been\Nused by them so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm a victim, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kick all of their asses already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:04:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Poison?\NThat woman is troublesome...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're something, Bege!\NYou turned into such a big castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Castle-Castle Fruit is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for that!\NThink about the situation we're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The assassination plot that we worked on for over a year\Nended in failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time we've failed to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the Emperor of the Sea proved\Nout of our league...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have that much time.\NI'll tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She stopped crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool, Bege, has betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Betrayal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This castle is me.\NIt's strong but not unbreakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they destroy the castle, I'll die.\NThen the castle will be gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once you guys get thrown out,\Nthe monsters will prey on you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel her anger...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're damned if you stay and damned if you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in dire straits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame it on me, Bege!\NThat launcher was the world's most advanced...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wh-What was that?\N--Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bege! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You bastards!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bege!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Straw Hat!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's looking at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom came to her senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:08:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, come out of the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourselves, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you betrayed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey! Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! I'm scared! I'm scared! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Bege! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Pez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama! It's me!\NBege's my husband and we have a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive him! Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look exactly like Lola as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attack is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back, Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to show your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you conspiring with them to kill me, too,\NChiffon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna live to eat\Ntomorrow's sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the castle is destroyed and Bege dies,\Nthey'll all be thrown out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anyone get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Firetank Pirates. The Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, Jimbei! Germa 66!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They messed up the wedding\Nand the Tea Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we've been taken so lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hang them up\Nto set an example for others!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that old bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with a cannon,\Nthe Big Father won't get a scratch,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but its defenses aren't a match for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to get out and kick her ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?! Hey! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Don't get carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to take back Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i},\Ndidn't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a copy of the Ponegliff
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and achieved Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i}'s wish\Nto save his family!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We accomplished our goals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have enough time to fight back,\Nthink about how we can escape instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we wanted to fight, we would've brought\NZoro and everyone else too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i}, Nami-{\i1}san{\i} is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it this far\Nbecause there are only a small number of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go to the Land of Wano safely\Nwhere Zoro-{\i1}san{\i}'s waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Bege is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege is getting attacked on our account!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy, good boy. Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our results are catastrophic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not willing to sit by\Nand watch your relish in your success!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Bege-{\i1}san{\i}!\NYou can't drag us down with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did what I had to do too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my heart now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drag you down...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't care about you guys at all\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my precious subordinates...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and my beloved wife and child are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for everyone to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not gonna last long...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to attack anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can crush them with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get rid of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...every one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come out already!\NThen, I'll keep you all in the mirror dimension!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to survive... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room in the Big Father...\Nis actually inside of my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how strongly we're attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether the Big Father leans or falls over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who'll get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you guys stay here,\Nyou're not gonna get affected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come to think of it...\N--It's only Bege-{\i1}san{\i} who is suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:15:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can hear Big Mom's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it remains calm inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it won't change\Neven if I turn back to my human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean,\Nwe'll be safe as long as we stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen... I'll change back to my human form\Nkeeping you guys inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Caesar will carry me and fly away\Nto escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it goes well, we can get out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How could you put my life in danger\Nwithout even asking me, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like digging our own grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get riddled with bullets in an instant!\NThere's no chance of success!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many users of the Color of Arms too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can turn into gas but it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know if there's any chance of success!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell unless you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only agile when you're escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, you fools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're hateful enemies to you\Nand we totally fell into the trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because my {\i1}father{\i} would be sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had stuck to my resentment\Nfrom my old days...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to be born weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd be disappointed in me\Nfor becoming such a small-minded rat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who'd laugh at your blood family's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna live a life in which I'm too ashamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to face him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever admit that I'm your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in front of other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that I don't want anyone to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You realize that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vinsmoke Sanji who escaped from Germa\Ndied once at sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So admit this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my father, Vinsmoke Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever show yourself in front of us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't approach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already did my part!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing more isn't part of our deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come out!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Honey!\N--Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be here anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done, you'll die too, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gang Bege!\NUntil you and Caesar Clown fly away into the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we Germa will escort you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you decide what I'm gonna do?!\NYour high-handed attitude hasn't changed, Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:20:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... You Germa people can fly too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll leave you behind, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, if we need to buy time, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's okay, Luffy.\N--But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be indebted to this "failure"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how they wanna settle it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait! Whoa-whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say I was gonna do this, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar Clown...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't ready at all from the beginning!\NYou guys should protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission is to let Caesar and Bege escape\Nquickly and safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a battle for evacuation.\NDefense is harder than offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to step out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting ready to step out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna deactivate the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Germa! Start attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Germa 66 join forces\Nand a deadly escape plan begins!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Mom's furious attacks raise Luffy's fighting spirit!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To prove himself as the future King of the Pirates,\Nhis special Gear Four techniques blast!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Escape From the Tea Party! Luffy vs. Big Mom!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
